  "title": "Architectural Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>ARCHITECTURAL ASSISTANT</strong></p><p>We are looking for <strong>Architectural Assistants</strong> with local experience to work on the architectural design, submissions and project management of projects.  </p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Work on/Assist with the architectural design and project management of projects</li><li>Work with Management, Clients, Consultants, Contractors and other stakeholders </li><li>Review and ensure compliance on local regulations, bylaws and building codes</li><li>Conduct research and analysis to ensure best possible outcome for the project</li><li>Project scheduling and budgeting</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Architecture</li><li>2-3 years’ experience working on commercial and residential projects and civic institutions</li><li>AutoCAD, Revit, 3D software, Microsoft Office</li><li>Knowledge of local building codes and regulations and Authority submission processes</li><li>Self-driven candidate with motivation and initiative</li><li>Singapore Citizen/PR</li></ul>",
