    "description": "<p>CGNARCHITECTS PTE. LTD.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>cgnArchitects was registered as a professional practice in 2007. &nbsp;Despite its short history, it has already made its mark by being appointed for major projects in Singapore and in the region.<br>\nThe strength of the practice lies in the cumulative wealth of experience in the team. &nbsp;This carefully selected group of architects and designers has worked in various types of developments; be it retail, landed residential estates, condominiums, high-rise office buildings, high-tech industrial plants, infrastructure and master-planning. &nbsp;This accumulated knowledge pool is our asset.<br>\nThe team members' past involvement in various overseas projects has helped to offer creative architectural ideas backed by practical considerations and technical know-how. <br>\nAs part of our expansion plan, we established companies in Kuala Lumpur &nbsp;&nbsp;and Shanghai to service the growing number of regional projects.<br>\n</p>",
